    <text>
        <body>
            <div type="edition" xml:space="preserve"><head>Text</head><ab><lb n="1"/>
                <expan><abbr>M</abbr><ex>arco</ex></expan> Iulio Hermesiano <lb n="2"/>diffusori oleario <lb n="3"/>patri pientissimo <lb n="4"/><expan><abbr>M</abbr><ex>arcus</ex></expan> Iulius Hermes Fron<lb break="no" n="5"/>tinianus <expan><abbr>fil</abbr><ex>ius</ex></expan> et <expan><abbr>M</abbr><ex>arcus</ex></expan> Iulius <lb n="6"/>Hermesianus <expan><abbr>nep</abbr><ex>os</ex></expan> <lb n="7"/>posuerunt <lb n="8"/>accepto loco ab splendidissimo ordine <expan><abbr>Astig</abbr><ex>itano</ex></expan>
            </ab></div>
            <div type="commentary">
                <p>Auf der Oberseite zwei Dübellöcher zur Befestigung einer Bronzestatue. Weißer Marmor mit violetten Adern. Datierung: wohl in die Herrschaftszeit des Septimius Severus.</p>
            </div>
